Package: LearnPCA
Type: Package
Title: Functions, Data Sets and Vignettes to Aid in Learning Principal Components Analysis (PCA)
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2022-05-01
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bryan A.", "Hanson",
